visible = true,\n            enter = fadeIn() + slideInVertically(),\n            exit = fadeOut() + slideOutVertically()\n        ) {\n            Column(\n                modifier = Modifier\n backgroundOpacity = 0.95f,\n                            borderOpacity = 0f,\n                            borderWidth = 0.dp,\n                            tintColor = Color.Black,\n                            tintOpacity = 0.8f\n                        ),\n                        depth = DepthLevel(1f)\n                    )\n                    .padding(24.dp)\n            ) {\n                // Header\n                HelpHeader(onDismiss = onDismiss)\n                \n                Spacer(modifier = Modifier.height(24.dp))\n                \n                // Category selection\n                CategorySelector(\n                    selectedCategory = _selectedCategory,\n                    onCategorySelected = { _selectedCategory = it }\n                )\n                \n                Spacer(modifier = Modifier.height(24.dp))\n                \n                // Command list\n                CommandList(\n                    category = _selectedCategory,\n                    searchQuery = _searchQuery\n                )\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n@Composable\nprivate fun HelpHeader(onDismiss: () -> Unit) {\n    Row(\n        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),\n        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween,\n        verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically\n    ) {\n        Column {\n            Text(\n                text = \"Voice Commands\",\n                style = MaterialTheme.typography.headlineMedium,\n                color = Color.White,\n                fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold\n            )\n            Text(\n                text = \"Say any command to control your device\",\n                style = MaterialTheme.typography.bodyLarge,\n                color = Color.White.copy(alpha = 0.7f)\n            )\n        }\n        \n        IconButton(\n            onClick = onDismiss,\n            modifier = Modifier\n                .glassMorphism(\n                    config = GlassMorphismDefaults.Button.copy(\n                        tintColor = Color(0xFFFF5722)\n                    ),\n                    depth = DepthLevel(0.4f)\n                )\n        ) {\n            Icon(\n                imageVector = Icons.Default.Close,\n                contentDescription = \"Close Help\",\n                tint = Color.White\n            )\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n@Composable\nprivate fun CategorySelector(\n    selectedCategory: HelpCategory,\n    onCategorySelected: (HelpCategory) -> Unit\n) {\n    LazyRow(\n        horizontalArrangement = isSelected: Boolean,\n    onClick: () -> Unit\n) {\n    Card(\n        modifier = Modifier\n            .clickable { onClick() }\n            .glassMorphism(\n                config = GlassMorphismConfig(\n                    cornerRadius = 20.dp,\n                    backgroundOpacity = if (isSelected) 0.25f else 0.1f,\n                    borderOpacity = if (isSelected) 0.4f else 0.2f,\n                    borderWidth = 1.dp,\n                    tintColor = category.color,\n                    tintOpacity = if (isSelected) 0.3f else 0.15f\n                ),\n                depth = DepthLevel(if (isSelected) 0.8f else 0.4f)\n            ),\n        colors = CardDefaults.cardColors(containerColor = Color.Transparent)\n    ) {\n        Row(\n            modifier = Modifier.padding(horizontal = 16.dp, vertical = 8.dp),\n            verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,\n            horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)\n        ) {\n            Icon(\n                imageVector = category.icon,\n                contentDescription = category.title,\n                modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp),\n                tint = if (isSelected) Color.White else Color.White.copy(alpha = 0.7f)\n            )\n            \n            Text(\n                text = category.title,\n                color = if (isSelected) Color.White else Color.White.copy(alpha = 0.7f),\n                fontSize = 14.sp,\n                fontWeight = if (isSelected) FontWeight.SemiBold else FontWeight.Normal\n            )\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n@Composable\nprivate fun CommandList(\n    category: HelpCategory,\n    @Suppress(\"UNUSED_PARAMETER\") searchQuery: String\n) {\n    val commands = remember(category) { getCommandsForCategory(category) }\n    \n    LazyColumn(\n        verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(12.dp)\n    ) {\n        items(commands) { commandGroup ->\n            CommandGroupCard(commandGroup = commandGroup)\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n@Composable\nprivate fun CommandGroupCard(commandGroup: CommandGroup) {\n    Card(\n        modifier = Modifier\n            .fillMaxWidth()\n            .glassMorphism(\n                config = GlassMorphismDefaults.Card,\n                depth = DepthLevel(0.6f)\n            ),\n        colors = CardDefaults.cardColors(containerColor = Color.Transparent)\n    ) {\n        Column(\n            modifier = Modifier.padding(16.dp)\n        ) {\n            Text(\n                text = commandGroup.title,\n                style = MaterialTheme.typography.titleMedium,\n                color = Color.White,\n                fontWeight = FontWeight.SemiBold\n            )\n            \n            Spacer(modifier = Modifier.height(8.dp))\n            \n            commandGroup.commands.forEach { command ->\n                CommandItem(command = command)\n                Spacer(modifier = Modifier.height(6.dp))\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n@Composable\nprivate fun CommandItem(command: VoiceCommand) {\n    Row(\n        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),\n        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween,\n        verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically\n    ) {\n        Column(\n            modifier = Modifier.weight(1f)\n        ) {\n            Text(\n                text = \"\\\"${command.phrase}\\\"\",\n                color = Color(0xFF4CAF50),\n                fontSize = 14.sp,\n                fontWeight = FontWeight.Medium\n            )\n            \n            if (command.description.isNotEmpty()) {\n                Text(\n                    text = command.description,\n                    color = Color.White.copy(alpha = 0.7f),\n                    fontSize = 12.sp\n                )\n            }\n        }\n        \n        if (command.alternatives.isNotEmpty()) {\n            Text(\n                text = \"+${command.alternatives.size} more\",\n                color = Color.White.copy(alpha = 0.5f),\n                fontSize = 10.sp\n            )\n        }\n    }\n}\n\n/**\n * Help categories for Icons.Default.Apps, Color(0xFFFF9800)),\n    CURSOR(\"Cursor\", Icons.Default.CenterFocusWeak, Color(0xFF00BCD4)),\n    INPUT(\"Input\", Icons.Default.Keyboard, Color(0xFF795548)),\n    HELP(\"Help\", Voice command discovery overlay\n│   └── utils/                  # UI utilities\n├── commands/                   # Browser command handlers\n└── README.md\n```\n\n## Components\n\n### HelpOverlay\nThe HelpOverlay component displays available voice commands organized by category:\n- **Navigation**: Browser navigation commands\n- **Tabs**: Tab management\n- **Zoom**: Zoom controls\n- **Features**: Bookmarks, history, downloads, settings\n- **Mode**: Reader mode, dark mode\n- **Scroll**: Page scrolling\n\n### Responsive Design\nThe overlay adapts to device orientation:\n- **Portrait**: Full-width layout with standard padding\n- **Landscape**: 85% width, centered, reduced padding for optimal content visibility\n\n## Platform Support\n\n| Platform | Status |\n|----------|--------|\n| Android  | Active |\n| iOS      | Planned |\n| Desktop  | Planned |\n\n## Integration\n\nWebAvanue integrates with:\n- VoiceOS for speech recognition\n- Common/UI for MagicUI components\n- Platform-specific browser engines\n\n## Development\n\n**Author**: WebAvanue Development Team\n**Created**: 2025-12-10\n**Status**: Active Development\n\n## Related Modules\n\n- VoiceOS: Core voice recognition system\n- Common/UI: Shared UI components\n- AvaConnect: Device connectivity\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":395,"cache_read_input_tokens":86351,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":395,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":715,"service_tier":"standard"},"context_management":{"applied_edits":[]}},"requestId":"req_011CVxvZJtinTHqYEm8KVwTp","type":"assistant","uuid":"a70eae2a-4a38-4554-8a17-5d713c47d159","timestamp":"2025-12-10T11:26:04.324Z"}
